data.description:
Beautiful Country Home with Acreage, Lamar County, NE Texas
Beautiful country retreat as closest neighbor is a mile away. Open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths. Homes sets off the road, back patio to enjoy yourcoffee, relax  entertain. Enough acreage with barn  2 stock ponds to run a few head of cattle. Or just enjoy the acreage  fish in the stocked ponds. Home is spacious with plenty of storage, great game/entertainment room to enjoy, large bedrooms, large living room with gas log fireplace for the winter time. Also has a chicken coop for your own country eggs  can include the chickens. Many recent updates: roof 10/22, HVAC 8/20 transferable warranty, new flooring 2017, water heaters, dishwasher  microwave/vent a hood 2020, fridge 2021, fencing 2017, gas log insert 2020. Alarm system for fire, medical  burglar 24 hr monitored. 80' WiFires tower high speed internet 2022. Ready to get out of the stress of the city  move to the country, this one is move in ready! Just 16 miles to Paris, TX, 34 miles to Mt. Pleasant, 100 miles to Dallas. Come see!
